  "subject": "sdnc/adaptors: Fixing site path for nexus",
  "commit_message": "sdnc/adaptors: Fixing site path for nexus\n\npom.xml specifies the wrong site url where the site:stage-deploy\nneeds to happen.\nThe site path in nexus to post to should match the repo name.\nIn this case, \"content/sites/site/org/onap/sdnc/adaptors/\"\n\nChange-Id: I5b413aeb94ab7895197ef944d9f2a51c04eff996\nSigned-off-by: Jessica Wagantall <jwagantall@linuxfoundation.org>\n",
